Subject: PATCH: Fix glitches in the git backend of vcs_info
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2009 16:25:54 +0200
Message-Id: <1245421554-4257-1-git-send-email-ft@bewatermyfriend.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 1.6.3.1.169.g33fd
